

    ● throw keyword is used
    to throw an exception explicitly

    ● throws keyword is used
    to declare an exception
    which means it works similar to the
    try--catch block
    ● throw new RuntimeException (“Invalid browser name!”) - throws ArithmeticException;
    We throw RuntimeException in the Driver class. You need to pass the driver’s name (chrome, firefox,etc.) if the text does not meet the available browser we want to throw an exception.
    public void deposit(double amount) throws RemoteException { // Method implementation
throw new RemoteException(); }